<br>
I have to agree with Micewandu.  IMO tanks are the ones who taunt mobs off on a regular basis.  I don't think clerics need to be chain healing me while I create constant aggro.  I will step in from time to time if enchanter is getting interrupted but that's in an emergency and is rare, even then I will root. I control my aggro and when the rare occasion I screw up and move to top of list I would rather have AC and not get hit at all.  If I'm getting hit for full damage (maybe 300 plus a round) no regen is going to save me.  Same goes for resists.  Most the time my health never ever goes down if I know the mobs well and how to not get aggrod on.<br>
